🧩 Challenge 2: Create a Top Announcement Strip
🎯 Task
Create a reusable strip component with a gradient background and display it above the Header on all pages.


📌 Requirements
1. Top Strip Component
* Create a component (e.g., TopStrip.jsx)
* Add:
  - Gradient background (any colors)
  - Centered text (example: "🔥 Admissions Open 2026")
  - Text should be clearly visible
-------------------------------------------------------------
2. Positioning (Important ⭐)
* Strip must be placed above the Header
* It should be visible on all pages
* Do NOT duplicate it in each page → place it in App.jsx
-------------------------------------------------------------
3. Styling
* Height: small (like a notification bar)
* Text aligned center
* Use CSS / Tailwind
-------------------------------------------------------------
🧪 Expected Behavior
- Strip is always visible
- Header appears below it
- Only page content changes on navigation
-------------------------------------------------------------